<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>EcoLife ‚Äì Carbon Awareness for Students</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <style>
        :root{
            --green:#2e7d32;
            --light:#f4faf5;
            --dark:#1c1c1c;
        }

        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing:border-box;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, sans-serif;
        }

        body{
            background:linear-gradient(180deg,#f7fff9,#ffffff);
            color:var(--dark);
        }

        header{
            display:flex;
            justify-content:space-between;
            align-items:center;
            padding:18px 8%;
        }

        header h2{
            font-weight:600;
            letter-spacing:0.5px;
        }

        header a{
            text-decoration:none;
            margin-left:12px;
            padding:8px 16px;
            border-radius:6px;
            font-size:14px;
            transition:0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn{
            background:var(--green);
            color:#fff;
        }

        .btn:hover{
            opacity:0.85;
        }

        .btn-outline{
            border:1px solid var(--green);
            color:var(--green);
            background:transparent;
        }

        .hero{
            min-height:80vh;
            display:flex;
            align-items:center;
            justify-content:center;
            text-align:center;
            padding:0 8%;
        }

        .hero-box{
            max-width:720px;
            animation:fadeUp 0.9s ease;
        }

        .hero h1{
            font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem);
            margin-bottom:16px;
            font-weight:700;
        }

        .hero p{
            font-size:1.05rem;
            line-height:1.7;
            opacity:0.85;
            margin-bottom:28px;
        }

        .hero-actions a{
            display:inline-block;
            margin:8px;
            padding:12px 28px;
            border-radius:8px;
            font-weight:500;
        }

        .features{
            padding:70px 8%;
            display:grid;
            grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));
            gap:24px;
        }

        .feature{
            background:var(--light);
            padding:28px;
            border-radius:14px;
            transition:transform 0.25s ease;
        }

        .feature:hover{
            transform:translateY(-6px);
        }

        .feature span{
            font-size:26px;
        }

        .feature h3{
            margin:14px 0 8px;
            font-size:1.1rem;
        }

        .feature p{
            font-size:0.95rem;
            opacity:0.8;
        }

        footer{
            text-align:center;
            padding:24px;
            font-size:0.85rem;
            opacity:0.7;
        }

        @keyframes fadeUp{
            from{
                opacity:0;
                transform:translateY(25px);
            }
            to{
                opacity:1;
                transform:translateY(0);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h2>üå± EcoLife</h2>
    <nav>
        <a href="login.html" class="btn-outline">Login</a>
        <a href="signup.html" class="btn">Create Account</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-box">
        <h1>Understand Your Impact.<br>Reduce It Thoughtfully.</h1>
        <p>
            EcoLife is a student-focused carbon awareness platform that
            turns everyday activities into clear environmental insights
            ‚Äî without complexity.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="signup.html" class="btn">Start Tracking</a>
            <a href="login.html" class="btn-outline">I already have an account</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="features">
    <div class="feature">
        <span>üìä</span>
        <h3>Personal Carbon Insights</h3>
        <p>Track emissions from daily habits with meaningful, readable data.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
        <span>üåç</span>
        <h3>Smarter Eco Choices</h3>
        <p>Receive practical suggestions tailored for student lifestyles.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature">
        <span>üìà</span>
        <h3>Progress You Can See</h3>
        <p>Visual reports that show improvement, not just numbers.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    ¬© 2026 EcoLife ¬∑ Built with intent for conscious students
</footer>

</body>
</html>
